				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13712568/scp-3743#post-4771334</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 10 Sep 2020 03:13:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><em>&#8230;aggressive conduct, if allowed to go unchecked and unchallenged, ultimately leads to war.</em></p> <p>- <strong>John F. Kennedy</strong></p> </blockquote> <p>This article follows from the events of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/cleaning-house">Cleaning House</a>, but should stand on its own.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">►&nbsp;Spoilers&nbsp;◄</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>Modern people have been living in SCP-3743-B.</li> <li>There are 13 sarcophagi and 13 winged humanoids.</li> <li>Are they cupids? You tell me.</li> <li>I am taking some artistic liberties with &quot;hundred handers&quot; traditionally called the Hecatoncheires. But by this point in the series, that should have been obvious.</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>If you are interested in my other works: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/grigori-karpin-s-author-page">Grigori Karpin's Author Page</a>, where you can see how these interconnected skips and tales fit into place. My goal is ever to have these articles stand on their own. But the relationships and information change over time, and that is reflected in the character's behavior.</p> <p>Thanks for Reading!</p> <p>Crit: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span><br /> Readers: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986843&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="Ralliston" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986843)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" >Ralliston</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yellowislol" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6284593&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="YellowISlol" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6284593)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yellowislol" >YellowISlol</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-00" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6766116&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="jack_00" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6766116)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jack-00" >jack_00</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedfox" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6797425&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="TwistedFox" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6797425)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedfox" >TwistedFox</a></span></p> <p>Special shoutout to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athenodora" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1272299&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998999" alt="Athenodora" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1272299)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athenodora" >Athenodora</a></span> for helping me with the Ancient Greek history aspects of this skip.</p> <p>I included it in the licensing box, but I quoted some translation of the Theogony sourced from Wikipedia, the link is in the licensing box.</p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/hecatoncheires-cycle-hub">Hecatoncheires Cycle</a></strong></p> </div> 
